comment: Solmee ! I thought a lot about you, seeing you didn’t upload videos made me think something wrong was happening to you so I wished you the best and sent you love by thoughts. It’s going to be okay I know you’ll be able to overcome what you’re going through. We all know that and we trust you  I think feeling burned out is something we’ll all experience at some point in our life so let’s support each other with compassion when that time comes
It's also inspiring showing your negative side and how you overcome it! It's very relatable and human. Be kind to yourself <3 the sun will soon shine again :)

Dear Solmi, I want to thank you so much!  This summer I watched old videos every day, they inspired me to love myself and take care of myself!  I'm very grateful!
  You are a person with good energy!
  It's okay to burn out, it's okay to be weak, it's sad, but it's our life, it's impossible to move forward without stopping!
  I love you very much, thank you for coming back
